content_sections.content:
Learn how to style an hr element with CSS.
How To Style HR
Horizontal Line
You can use the
border
property to style a
hr
element:
Example
/* Red border */
hr.new1 {
border-top: 1px solid red;
}
/* Dashed red 
  border */
hr.new2 {
border-top: 1px dashed red;
}
/* Dotted red border */
hr.new3 {
border-top: 1px dotted red;
}
/* Thick red border */
hr.new4 {
border: 1px solid red;
}
/* Large rounded 
  green border */
hr.new5 {
border: 10px solid green;
border-radius: 5px;
}

